Summary: Methods for manipulating 3D concave polygon shape faces

- get_faces() → PackedVector3Array (const): Returns the array of face vertices defining the concave polygon shape
- set_faces(faces: PackedVector3Array): Sets the face vertices defining the concave polygon shape. Accepts a PackedVector3Array containing vertex data for all faces.
